Class NucEditModel

java.lang.Object
  org.rhwlab.nucedit.NucEditModel
public class NucEditModel
extends java.lang.Object

responds to menu commands on the edit dialog and makes the requested changes in the nuclei vector of NucleiMgr
holds an array of NucleiTableModel objects which are potentially editable by the user
